Architecture: all
Depends: debconf, docker.io | docker-ce, docker-compose-v2 | docker-compose-plugin
Maintainer: voidnery <opensource@voidnery.pro>
Homepage: https://github.com/__OWNER__/nnm-control
Description: NNM Control (network-nimble-media-control) — web panel for Nimble Streamer
 Self-hosted management panel for Nimble Streamer instances using their
 native management API. Runs as a Docker Compose stack (MongoDB + Node.js
 API + React UI behind nginx) managed by a systemd unit.
